ded application into the January 2024 course, students can now check and receive their offer letter. This is to let students know her to prepare for lectures beginning soon.<\/p>\n<p>See Also: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-login-to-ustboniface-student-portal\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">How to login to USTBoniface student portal<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-is-included-in-the-offer-letter-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_Included_in_the_Offer_Letter_2024\"><\/span>What is Included in the Offer Letter 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Important information about your Degree Program, Scholarship offer (if applicable), Financial Assistance, Residence, and more is included with your offer. Any conditions associated with your offer will appear in your offer letter.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/d3lut3gzcpx87s.cloudfront.net\/image_encoded\/aHR0cHM6Ly9zaWxrc3RhcnQuczMuYW1hem9uYXdzLmNvbS8wOGQ4NTgyOS0xMTFmLTQ5YjgtODhhZC1mMDU0ODE1M2M0N2MuanBn\/560x292\" alt=\"Universit\u00e9 de Saint-Boniface Offer Letter\" width=\"424\" height=\"221\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-accept-the-offer-letter-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Accept_the_Offer_Letter_2024\"><\/span>How to Accept the Offer Letter\u00a0 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To accept the admission offers and download acceptance letter, follow this instructions below, pay deposit fees as indicated.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Log on to the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/ustboniface.ca\/admission\/etat-demande-admission\" class=\"broken_link\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Application Portal<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Click Accept Admission Offer<\/li>\n<li>Download the Offer Letter.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>For more information, kindly send us a feedback message and we will attend to you in a moment.<\/p>\n<p>See Also: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/ustboniface-fall-academic-calendar-2024\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">USTBoniface Winter Academic Calendar 2024 | Universit\u00e9 de Saint-Boniface<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Was the information useful? Like and share this post.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Universit\u00e9 de Saint-Boniface Offer Letter 2024, Acceptance, Monitor\/Track Application Status, Application Deadlines, Application Portal. Universit\u00e9 de Saint-Boniface \u2013&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[772],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6270"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6270"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6270\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":19189,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6270\/revisions\/19189"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6270"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=6270"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=6270"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}